The paper deals with the achievable degrees of freedom (DoF) in a multi-cell interference channel, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT). The use of feedback channels is also a common theme in networking (cs.NI) and signal processing (cs.SI). The paper also discusses the quantization of feedback information, which is a topic in multimedia (cs.MM) and machine learning (cs.LG).
